    {
      "id": "41fa8595-5974-48af-8a73-5377e319f90d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Despite its utility, online learning is carachterized by unusually high dropout rates, which is counterintuitive to the notion of making education more accessible. Ther are systems nowadays that allow for early identification.",
